flowRoot.flowPara: Includes performance, stability and security improvements.

If there are only offline updates, a restart & install button is shown in the header bar. We might want to use a requires restart banner for this state in the future, if we get to the point where most updates are atomic.
If a firmware update requires additional steps before the upgrade can take place, a message dialog is shown. The update button becomes sensitive once the device is ready.
To update firmware, your X100 mouse needs to be in update mode.
Press and hold the power button for three seconds. The light will flash when in update mode. You can then install.
